  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Description\r\n\r\nSwitching channels feels laggy because the pending animation is missing.\r\n\r\nBy pending animation I mean:\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/117639195/229799428-9eb82df3-5d4c-4d15-8b7b-00ed63208805.mov\r\n\r\n\r\n## Steps to reproduce\r\n\r\nSwitch channels in any community\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n\r\nChannel switches immediately with optional pending animation\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n\r\nChannel switches with ~1sec lag without pending animation\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status desktop version: 0.14.0\r\n- Operating System: Fedora\r\n\r\n",
