    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "From what I investigated, there's a ~1s delay even when switching between _already loaded_ channels.\r\n\r\nThis is happening because of `ExpressionRole` here:\r\nhttps://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/blob/2d0047846739f076510378327ecbff85b05154f3/ui/app/AppLayouts/Chat/panels/UserListPanel.qml#L63-L70\r\n\r\nwhich is used for sorting here:\r\nhttps://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/blob/2d0047846739f076510378327ecbff85b05154f3/ui/app/AppLayouts/Chat/panels/UserListPanel.qml#L76-L79\r\n\r\nCommenting these lines makes channel switching quite fast, we don't need animation there.\r\n\r\ncc @alexandraB99, I think UI team knows better how to deal with this?\r\nCan you please pick it up?\r\n\r\n-----\r\n\r\nWe do though need animation when switching to a not-yet-cached channel. \r\nI'm looking into this now.",
